just go back to Brenda

44:25.996 --> 44:28.290
and forget everything
that happened?

44:29.333 --> 44:31.377
We'll always have Paris.

44:31.460 --> 44:34.004
It is not funny anymore.

44:37.966 --> 44:41.512
I guess nothing lasts forever.

44:44.681 --> 44:46.683
Kelly...

44:48.477 --> 44:51.480
(waves crashing)
